al markets through deep AI analysis.\\\",\\\"hero_desc\\\":\\\"Real-time multi-faceted market analysis powered by advanced proprietary algorithms. We integrate on-chain data, macroeconomic indicators, and institutional sentiment to provide highly transparent intelligence.\\\",\\\"terminal_access\\\":\\\"Terminal Access\\\",\\\"latest_reports\\\":\\\"Latest Reports\\\",\\\"signal_analysis_title\\\":\\\"Real-time Signal Analysis\\\",\\\"view_all_signals\\\":\\\"View all signals\\\",\\\"feature_terminal_title\\\":\\\"Market Terminal\\\",\\\"feature_terminal_desc\\\":\\\"Millisecond-level tick data updates and AI predictions. All the infrastructure professionals need, integrated into a single refined interface.\\\",\\\"view_details\\\":\\\"View Details\\\",\\\"feature_risk_title\\\":\\\"Risk Management Protocol\\\",\\\"feature_risk_desc\\\":\\\"Not just high-probability AI entries, but a rock-solid foundation for growth with multi-layered stop-loss algorithms to minimize drawdowns.\\\",\\\"performance\\\":\\\"Performance\\\"},\\\"signals\\\":{\\\"target\\\":\\\"Analysis Target\\\",\\\"buy\\\":\\\"Strong Buy\\\",\\\"sell\\\":\\\"Strong Sell\\\",\\\"neutral\\\":\\\"Neutral\\\",\\\"entry\\\":\\\"Entry\\\",\\\"tp\\\":\\\"Take Profit (TP)\\\",\\\"sl\\\":\\\"Stop Loss (SL)\\\",\\\"details\\\":\\\"In-depth Analysis\\\",\\\"start_trading\\\":\\\"Start Trading\\\",\\\"modal_title\\\":\\\"{pair} Signal Deep Analysis\\\",\\\"current_trend\\\":\\\"Current Trend\\\",\\\"uptrend\\\":\\\"Strong Uptrend\\\",\\\"downtrend\\\":\\\"Strong Downtrend\\\",\\\"range\\\":\\\"Range / Consolidation\\\",\\\"confidence\\\":\\\"AI Confidence Score\\\",\\\"engine_commentary\\\":\\\"AI Inference Engine Commentary\\\",\\\"strategy\\\":\\\"Recommended Strategy\\\",\\\"tp_target\\\":\\\"Take Profit Target\\\",\\\"sl_limit\\\":\\\"Stop Loss Limit\\\",\\\"analysis_desc_buy\\\":\\\"Solid support levels confirmed. High probability of mid-term rebound based on multi-dimensional correlation analysis of market