te differentials are the primary driver.\\\",\\\"jpy_theme_title\\\":\\\"JPY Market Theme\\\",\\\"jpy_theme_desc\\\":\\\"Seeking exit from negative interest rates. Focus on BoJ policy reversal timing. Key is the virtuous cycle of wages and prices.\\\",\\\"sentiment_radar\\\":\\\"Market Sentiment Radar\\\",\\\"sentiment_bullish\\\":\\\"Bullish\\\",\\\"sentiment_neutral\\\":\\\"Neutral\\\",\\\"sentiment_bearish\\\":\\\"Bearish\\\",\\\"sentiment_desc\\\":\\\"Real-time analysis of SNS, news, and options market skews using proprietary AI. Predicting market direction one step ahead of the crowd.\\\",\\\"vola_scanner\\\":\\\"Volatility Scanner\\\",\\\"vola_high\\\":\\\"High\\\",\\\"vola_mid\\\":\\\"Mid\\\",\\\"vola_low\\\":\\\"Low\\\",\\\"vola_desc\\\":\\\"Instantly detect volatility anomalies. Capture signs of trend reversals or sudden price shifts by measuring deviations from statistical means.\\\",\\\"correlation_matrix\\\":\\\"Correlation Assets Matrix\\\",\\\"corr_pair\\\":\\\"Pair\\\",\\\"corr_coeff\\\":\\\"Coeff\\\",\\\"corr_status\\\":\\\"Status\\\",\\\"corr_strong_pos\\\":\\\"Strong Positive\\\",\\\"corr_mid_pos\\\":\\\"Moderate Positive\\\",\\\"corr_strong_neg\\\":\\\"Strong Negative\\\",\\\"corr_weak_pos\\\":\\\"Weak Positive\\\",\\\"corr_desc\\\":\\\"Dynamic correlation between major pairs and macro assets (rates, commodities, indices). Determining if current theme is Rates or Risk-Off.\\\",\\\"sync_rate\\\":\\\"Synapse Sync Rate\\\",\\\"consistency_alert\\\":\\\"Inconsistency Alert: {level}\\\",\\\"view_details\\\":\\\"Deep Analysis →\\\",\\\"modal_terminal_details\\\":\\\"Synapse Terminal Details\\\",\\\"current_status\\\":\\\"Current Status\\\",\\\"sync_consistency\\\":\\\"Sync Consistency\\\",\\\"mtf_analysis\\\":\\\"Multi-Timeframe Analysis\\\",\\\"bullish_edge\\\":\\\"Bullish Edge\\\",\\\"bearish_edge\\\":\\\"Bearish Edge\\\",\\\"neutral_edge\\\":\\\"Neutral\\\",\\\"ai_diagnosis\\\":\\\"Synapse AI Diagnosis\\\",\\\"diagnosis_high\\\":\\\"Fewer inconsistencies, expecting price action following technical indicators.\\\",\\\"diagnosis_low\\\":\\\"Noise detected in some indicators, caution for sudden volatility. AI detects attempts to break resistance.\\\",\\\"status_stable\\\":\\\"Stable\\\",\\\"status_syncing\\\":\\\"Syncing\\\",\\\"status_in_progress\\\":\\\"In Progress\\\",\\\"status_divergent\\\":\\\"Divergent\\\",\\\"cons_high\\\":\\\"High\\\",\\\"cons_mid\\\":\\\"Mid\\\",\\\"cons_low\\\":\\\"Low\\\",\\\"diagnosis_text\\\":\\\"The Synapse AI engine has analyzed {pair} with a synchronization rate of {sync}%. The current diagnosis indicates: {detail}\\\",\\\"usd_theme_desc_title\\\":\\\"US Rate Expectations\\\",\\\"jpy_theme_desc_title\\\":\\\"BoJ Policy Pivot\\\"},\\\"crypto_pro\\\":{\\\"hero_badge\\\":\\\"Crypto Intelligence v2.4 Live\\\",\\\"hero_title\\\":\\\"AI thoroughly analyzes the crypto market.\\\",\\\"hero_desc\\\":\\\"From BTC to SOL, covering everything from major tickers to emerging L1s. AI monitors whale movements and DEX volume to capture the waves of volatility.\\\",\\\"terminal_title\\\":\\\"Crypto Synapse Terminal\\\",\\\"onchain_synced\\\":\\\"On-chain Synced\\\",\\\"advanced_analysis_layer\\\":\\\"Advanced Analysis Layer\\\",\\\"market_inter_sync\\\":\\\"Inter-market Sync Analysis\\\",\\\"btc_vs_us10y_title\\\":\\\"BTC vs US 10Y\\\",\\\"btc_vs_us10y_desc\\\":\\\"BTC's hedge function in a rising rate environment is declining. Correlation as a risk asset is becoming clearer.\\\",\\\"onchain_pulse\\\":\\\"On-chain Pulse\\\",\\\"whale_accumulation_title\\\":\\\"Whale Accumulation Status\\\",\\\"whale_accumulation_desc\\\":\\\"Inflow to major exchanges is decreasing. Whales' transfer to cold wallets is accelerating, suggesting supply shortage.\\\",\\\"liquidity_depth\\\":\\\"Market Liquidity Depth\\\",\\\"depth_range\\\":\\\"{range} Depth\\\",\\\"bid_side\\\":\\\"Bids\\\",\\\"ask_side\\\":\\\"Asks\\\",\\\"liquidity_desc\\\":\\\"Integrated analysis of CEX order books in milliseconds. Visualizing 'order book depth' that captures institutional moves and effective slippage during sudden moves.\\\",\\\"node_network_pulse\\\":\\\"Node Network Pulse\\\",\\\"network_load\\\":\\\"Network Load\\\",\\\"network_stable\\\":\\\"Stable\\\",\\\"avg_gas_price\\\":\\\"Avg Gas Price\\\",\\\"node_desc\\\":\\\"Analysis of transaction density, average gas prices, and mempool across mainnet and L1/L2 layers. Measuring blockchain health and on-chain demand intensity.\\\",\\\"whale_tracking\\\":\\\"On-chain Whale Tracking (Real-time Feed)\\\",\\\"whale_desc\\\":\\\"Extracting and tracking large on-chain transactions over $1M in real time. Monitoring exchange inflows (sell pressure) and outflows (return to long-term holding).\\\",\\\"whale_type_inflow\\\":\\\"Inflow\\\",\\\"whale_type_outflow\\\":\\\"Outflow\\\",\\\"whale_type_staking\\\":\\\"Staking\\\",\\\"whale_target_cold\\\":\\\"Cold Wallet\\\",\\\"whale_target_protocol\\\":\\\"Protocol\\\",\\\"modal_crypto_deep\\\":\\\"Crypto Synapse Deep Analysis\\\",\\\"market_consistency\\\":\\\"Market Consistency\\\",\\\"onchain_liquidity_matrix\\\":\\\"On-chain \\u0026 Liquidity Matrix\\\",\\\"volatility\\\":\\\"Volatility\\\",\\\"vola_active\\\":\\\"Active\\\",\\\"vola_stable\\\":\\\"Stable\\\",\\\"ai_onchain_diagnosis\\\":\\\"AI On-chain Diagnosis Report\\\",\\\"onchain_high\\\":\\\"Low noise, in a region where technical rebound can be expected.\\\",\\\"onchain_low\\\":\\\"Overall market volatility is rising, caution for sudden slippage is needed.\\\",\\\"onchain_diagnosis_text\\\":\\\"Currently, {pair} shows a synchronization of {sync}% between on-chain behavior and price action. {detail}\\\"},\\\"stocks_pro\\\":{\\\"hero_badge\\\":\\\"Global Equities Terminal v2.4 Live\\\",\\\"hero_title\\\":\\\"AI uncovers stock market alpha.\\\",\\\"hero_desc\\\":\\\"Integrating real-time PER, PBR, and short-term trading signals for S\\u0026P 500, Nikkei 225, and major European stocks. The same perspective as institutional investors, right at your finge