e_desc\":\"Analysis of transaction density, average gas prices, and mempool across mainnet and L1/L2 layers. Measuring blockchain health and on-chain demand intensity.\",\"whale_tracking\":\"On-chain Whale Tracking (Real-time Feed)\",\"whale_desc\":\"Extracting and tracking large on-chain transactions over $1M in real time. Monitoring exchange inflows (sell pressure) and outflows (return to long-term holding).\",\"whale_type_inflow\":\"Inflow\",\"whale_type_outflow\":\"Outflow\",\"whale_type_staking\":\"Staking\",\"whale_target_cold\":\"Cold Wallet\",\"whale_target_protocol\":\"Protocol\",\"modal_crypto_deep\":\"Crypto Synapse Deep Analysis\",\"market_consistency\":\"Market Consistency\",\"onchain_liquidity_matrix\":\"On-chain & Liquidity Matrix\",\"volatility\":\"Volatility\",\"vola_active\":\"Active\",\"vola_stable\":\"Stable\",\"ai_onchain_diagnosis\":\"AI On-chain Diagnosis Report\",\"onchain_high\":\"Low noise, in a region where technical rebound can be expected.\",\"onchain_low\":\"Overall market volatility is rising, caution for sudden slippage is needed.\",\"onchain_diagnosis_text\":\"Currently, {pair} shows a synchronization of {sync}% between on-chain behavior and price action. {detail}\"},\"stocks_pro\":{\"hero_badge\":\"Global Equities Terminal v2.4 Live\",\"hero_title\":\"AI uncovers stock market alpha.\",\"hero_desc\":\"Integrating real-time PER, PBR, and short-term trading signals for S&P 500, Nikkei 225, and major European stocks. The same perspective as institutional investors, right at your fingertips.\",\"terminal_title\":\"Stocks Synapse Terminal\",\"market_data_synced\":\"Market Data Synced\",\"pro_indicators\":\"Pro Indicators\",\"sector_heatmap\":\"Sector Heatmap\",\"earnings_radar\":\"Earnings Radar\",\"ai_momentum\":\"AI Momentum\",\"sector_semi\":\"Semiconductors\",\"sector_tech\":\"Technology\",\"sector_ev\":\"EV / Auto\",\"table_ticker\":\"Ticker\",\"table_date\":\"Date\",\"table_sentiment\":\"AI Sentiment\",\"sent_extreme_bull\":\"Extremely Bullish\",\"sent_neutral\":\"Neutral\",\"sent_caution\":\"Caution Needed\",\"overbought\":\"Overbought\",\"bullish\":\"Bullish\",\"golden_cross\":\"Golden Cross\",\"aligned\":\"Aligned\",\"alpha_scouter\":\"AI Alpha Scouter\",\"bull_divergence\":\"Bull Divergence Continued\",\"bottom_fishing\":\"Bottom Fishing\",\"box_breakout\":\"Box Breakout\",\"alpha_score\":\"Alpha Score\",\"alpha_desc\":\"Quantifying future excess returns (Alpha) from the perspective of profitability, growth, and supply-demand using a proprietary multi-factor model. AI scouts promising investment targets.\",\"institutional_flow\":\"Institutional & Large Flow Analysis\",\"net_inflow\":\"Net Inflow\",\"weekly\":\"Weekly\",\"flow_desc\":\"AI monitors dark pool and block trade flows that don't appear in normal quotes. Visually depicting the accumulation (buying) and distribution (selling) of smart money.\",\"sector_dispersion\":\"Sector Dispersion Analysis\",\"disp_high\":\"High\",\"disp_mid\":\"Mid\",\"disp_low\":\"Low\",\"risk_concentration\":\"Concentrated\",\"risk_stable\":\"Stable\",\"risk_high_vola\":\"High Vola\",\"disp_desc\":\"Dynamically measuring the divergence of individual stock price movements within each sector. Determining if the overall market is a 'Beta market' moving in the same direction, or an 'Alpha market' where stock selection is key.\",\"market_rank\":\"Market Rank\",\"est_per\":\"Est. PER\",\"ai_eval_breakout\":\"AI Eval: Breakout Expected\",\"modal_stock_deep\":\"Stock Deep Analysis Report\",\"valuation_metrics\":\"Valuation Metrics\",\"momentum_diagnosis\":\"Momentum Diagnosis\",\"prev_day_ratio\":\"Prev Day Ratio\",\"ai_investment_verdict\":\"AI Investment Verdict\",\"investment_verdict_text\":\"{ticker} currently maintains an extremely high relative advantage in the {type} sector. AI algorithm judges the recent rise with volume as 'accumulation by large investors'. A breakout of the upper resistance line is likely in the short term, suggestively transitioning to a 