\":\"Bids\",\"ask_side\":\"Asks\",\"liquidity_desc\":\"Integrated analysis of CEX order books in milliseconds. Visualizing 'order book depth' that captures institutional moves and effective slippage during sudden moves.\",\"node_network_pulse\":\"Node Network Pulse\",\"network_load\":\"Network Load\",\"network_stable\":\"Stable\",\"avg_gas_price\":\"Avg Gas Price\",\"node_desc\":\"Analysis of transaction density, average gas prices, and mempool across mainnet and L1/L2 layers. Measuring blockchain health and on-chain demand intensity.\",\"whale_tracking\":\"On-chain Whale Tracking (Real-time Feed)\",\"whale_desc\":\"Extracting and tracking large on-chain transactions over $1M in real time. Monitoring exchange inflows (sell pressure) and outflows (return to long-term holding).\",\"whale_type_inflow\":\"Inflow\",\"whale_type_outflow\":\"Outflow\",\"whale_type_staking\":\"Staking\",\"whale_target_cold\":\"Cold Wallet\",\"whale_target_protocol\":\"Protocol\",\"modal_crypto_deep\":\"Crypto Synapse Deep Analysis\",\"market_consistency\":\"Market Consistency\",\"onchain_liquidity_matrix\":\"On-chain & Liquidity Matrix\",\"volatility\":\"Volatility\",\"vola_active\":\"Active\",\"vola_stable\":\"Stable\",\"ai_onchain_diagnosis\":\"AI On-chain Diagnosis Report\",\"onchain_high\":\"Low noise, in a region where technical rebound can be expected.\",\"onchain_low\":\"Overall market volatility is rising, caution for sudden slippage is needed.\",\"onchain_diagnosis_text\":\"Currently, {pair} shows a synchronization of {sync}% between on-chain behavior and price action. {detail}\"},\"stocks_pro\":{\"hero_badge\":\"Global Equities Terminal v2.4 Live\",\"hero_title\":\"AI uncovers stock market alpha.\",\"hero_desc\":\"Integrating real-time PER, PBR, and short-term trading signals for S&P 500, Nikkei 225, and major European stocks. The same perspective as institutional investors, right at your fingertips.\",\"terminal_title\":\"Stocks Synapse Terminal\",\"market_data_synced\":\"Market 